## 6. Summary Checklist

For every data operation, ensure:

### Data Retrieval:
- [ ] Fetched in Server Component (not Client Component)
- [ ] Uses Clerk authentication (`await auth()`)
- [ ] Filters by authenticated `userId`
- [ ] Uses Drizzle ORM with schema imports

### Data Mutations:
- [ ] Implemented as Server Action (marked with `"use server"`)
- [ ] Has Zod validation schema defined
- [ ] Parameter type inferred from schema (`z.infer<>`)
- [ ] Input validated with `.parse()` or `.safeParse()`
- [ ] NOT using `FormData` as parameter type
- [ ] Uses Clerk authentication and ownership checks
- [ ] Calls `revalidatePath()` after mutation

### Client Integration:
- [ ] Client Components call Server Actions with typed objects
- [ ] Uses `useTransition` or `useFormStatus` for pending states
- [ ] Handles errors appropriately
- [ ] Optional: uses react-hook-form with zodResolver

