## 7. File Organization

```
app/
├── actions/
│   ├── deck-actions.ts      # Server Actions for decks
│   └── card-actions.ts      # Server Actions for cards
├── decks/
│   └── page.tsx             # Server Component (data fetching)
└── components/
    └── create-deck-form.tsx # Client Component (calls actions)

lib/
└── validations/
    ├── common.ts            # Shared validation schemas
    ├── deck-validations.ts  # Deck-specific schemas
    └── card-validations.ts  # Card-specific schemas
```

---

**Remember:** 
- **Read** in Server Components
- **Write** via Server Actions
- **Validate** everything with Zod
- **Type** all inputs (no `FormData` type)